entry.def: If you refer to a group of people as the nobs, you mean they are rich or come from a much higher social class than you do.

example.ex: ...the nobs who live in the Big House...
example.tran: 住在深宅大院里的有钱人

example.ex: I'm not tellin' you. Not now you're in with the nobs.
example.tran: 我不打算告诉你。你现在跟上流社会的人来往，我不会说的。
